messages.messageBody:
In a message dated 10/27/02 8:55:07 AM, starsuncloud@... writes:

<< And here's a BIG BONUS!!! I didn't know this until right this minute, but
both my boys fell on that ramp during the conference.
They told me just now when my dh asked what I was writing about.
Jared fell and landed on his back.
Trevor said he landed on his butt. AND he fell into the door at a later time
because of all the wetness around the whole area.
So there's some witnesses for ya! >>

OH MY!!!!!!

Just reading that made my stomach jump and then made my leg hurt.

This is really really bad.

A couple of times since I've been home I've thought clearly of that moment
when I went down and have cried really, really hard. I SO MUCH was ready to
kick off that conference and I hadn't looked forward to anything as much as I
was that for a long time.

Sandra
